            </mml:mover>
          </mml:semantics>
        </mml:math>
      </inline-formula> [cm<sup>&#x2013;1</sup>] = 2992 (w); 2365 (m); 1275 (m); 750 (s).</p>
      <p><sup>1</sup>H-NMR (600 MHz, DMSO-d<sub>6</sub>): &#x3B4; [ppm] = 8.26 (t, <italic>J</italic> = 7.6 Hz, 2H), 8.34 (d, <italic>J</italic> = 9.2 Hz, 2H), 8.41 (d, <italic>J</italic> = 8.9 Hz, 2H), 8.45 (d, <italic>J</italic> = 8.9 Hz, 2H), 8.53 (m, 6H), 8.64 (s, 4H), 8.78 (d, <italic>J</italic> = 1.3 Hz, 2H, H<sub>imidazole</sub>), 10.50 (t, <italic>J</italic> = 1.3 Hz, 1H, H<sub>imidazole</sub>).</p>
      <p><sup>13</sup>C-NMR (150 MHz, DMSO-d<sub>6</sub>): &#x3B4; [ppm] = 120.8 (+), 123.2 (q), 124.1 (q), 125.0 (+), 125.2 (q), 125.8 (+), 125.9 (q), 126.7 (+), 127.0 (+), 127.1 (+), 127.5 (+), 128.1 (q), 129.5 (+), 130.2 (+), 130.3 (+), 130.7 (q), 132.5 (q), 139.9 (+).</p>
      <p>HRMS calcd. for C<sub>35</sub>H<sub>21</sub>N<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup> [M<sup>+</sup>]: 469.1699. Found: 469.1703.</p>
      <p>UV/VIS (DMSO): &#x3BB;<sub>max</sub> [nm] (lg &#x3B5;) = 279 (4.794); 332 (4.570); 348 (4.722).</p>
